\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 3. H.} × {\b viridifolium} Peter, {\i Bot. Jahrb.}{\b  5}: 258 (1884) ({\i H. latisquamum} Naegeli & Peter, nom. illegit.; {\i H. hoppeanum} /{\i  lactucella}). Intermediate between the parents, but variable. Like {\i H. hoppeanum} but leaves more glaucous; capitula 2-3(-5), on long peduncles; involucral bracts 6-9 mm, narrower. Differs from {\i H. lactucella} in its thicker stolons, larger leaves which have dense stellate hairs beneath, and larger capitula. 1700-2500{\i  m. • C. Europe, extending to C. Jugoslavia.} Au Ge He Hu It Ju Rm.
