\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 4. H}. × {\b hypeuryum} Peter,{\i  Bot. Jahrb.}{\b  5}: 255 (1884) ({\i H. hoppeanum }/ {\i pilosella}). Like {\i H. hoppeanum} but with more numerous, longer, more slender stolons. 1400-2600 {\i m. S. & S.C. Europe.} Al Au Bu Ga Ge He Hs Hu It Ju Rs (K).
